    <briefdescription>
<para>CMA-ES - Covariance Matrix Adaptation Evolution Strategy is a stochastic search algorithm from the mlpack C++ library. It works by estimating a positive definite matrix within an iterative procedure using the covariance matrix. In this instance, the batchSize is fixed (= 1), and SelectionPolicy is also fixed (= FullSelection). </para>
    </briefdescription>
